item.title: Eny 1 know coords for empty land? + how 2 add ::tele command
item.dc:creator: @Omerata Omerata
item.description:
@Omerata wrote:

Say if you want ::varrock that is the codes.

if (command.startsWith("varrock")) { sendMessage("You arrive in varrock."); teleportToX = 3210; teleportToY = 3424; }

But for an empty one, here.

if (command.startsWith("Your Destination")) 
{ 
	sendMessage("You arrive in where ever you chose."); *It can be edited to say anything.*
	teleportToX = ####; //replace #### with X coords here. 
	teleportToY = ####; //replace #### with Y coords here.
}

I hope this helps you.=]
